type: TS LF Trading Bot Error - Execution Unexpected Error

definition.text: An Unexpected Error occurred while processing the execution of orders. The LF Trading Bot continued running after reporting this error.

paragraphs.text: The error prevented the LF Trading Bot from performing certain operations.
